@GovMurphy We don't know what this is yet.  
We don't have accurate testing.
We have changed the diagnostic parameters to inflate #Covid19 numbers and fatalities.
We KNOW it primarily impacts a vulnerable population.
And we KNOW there are repercussions to #StayAtHome.
